title: Week 7 preview & Patriots vs. Jets recap
itunes:title: Week 7 preview & Patriots vs. Jets recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every game on the Week 7 NFL schedule and recap the Patriots' close win over the Jets.
